## Summary Rules

1. ❌ **NO auto-install** optimization plugins without manual testing
2. ❌ **NO wp eval** for plugin configuration (use Admin UI)
3. ❌ **NO broad CSS overrides** (use specific selectors)
4. ✅ **YES baseline metrics** before changes
5. ✅ **YES immediate visual check** after activation
6. ✅ **YES Test Mode** when available
7. ✅ **YES one change at a time** with verification

**Default action for optimization plugins:** Leave with default settings, configure manually via UI, or don't install at all if Seraphinite/similar already active.

